{"type":"META","ticket":364,"id":"META"}||{"title":"L298N_C19922","tags":["电机驱动芯片","步进电机驱动芯片"],"source":"e028894a6ba446ea983ac7bdddb66ada|0819f05c4eef4c71ace90d822a990e87","images":["https://alimg.szlcsc.com/upload/public/product/middle/20221228/5024C50F8A385293403F04481E6C271A.jpg"],"attributes":{"LCSC Part Name":"双全桥驱动器","Supplier Part":"C19922","Manufacturer":"ST(意法半导体)","Manufacturer Part":"L298N","Supplier Footprint":"MultiwAtt-15","JLCPCB Part Class":"Extended Part","Datasheet":"https://item.szlcsc.com/datasheet/L298N/20631.html","Supplier":"LCSC","Add into BOM":"yes","Convert to PCB":"yes","Symbol":"db69dc4fad4cd6f1","Designator":"U?","Footprint":"5a27b9a0fa831764","3D Model":"17dbda3c803a45a0ac2c74e6ab5d5790|0819f05c4eef4c71ace90d822a990e87","3D Model Title":"MULTIWATT-15_L19.6-W5.0-P1.27-L","3D Model Transform":"795.27392,389.3693,0,0,0,0,0,84.646,-137.795","Control Voltage":"4.5V~7V","Motor Drive Voltage(Vm)":"-","Output Current":"2A","Number of H-bridges":"2","Drive Type":"双极驱动","Step Resolution":"-","Interface":"-","Technology":"-","RDS(on)":"-","Operating Temperature":"-25℃~+130℃","Name":"={Manufacturer Part}","Description":"L298 是一款采用 15 引脚 Multiwatt 和 PowerSO20 封装的单片集成电路。它是一款高压、大电流双路全桥驱动器，设计用于接收标准 TTL 逻辑电平，并驱动继电器、螺线管、直流和步进电机等感性负载。提供两个使能输入，可独立于输入信号启用或禁用该器件。每个桥路的下晶体管发射极连接在一起，相应的外部端子可用于连接外部检测电阻。还提供了一个额外的电源输入，使逻辑电路能在较低电压下工作。"}}|
